  "texts": [
    "The only difference is the single-qubit rotation angles.",
    "SP+CSP Multi-CopyIn order to prepare the joint state in Eq.",
    "That is, we first prepare the statew-1 d=0 U d(SP) |0 n ⟩ ⊗w = w-1 d=0 (|ϕ d ⟩ ⊗ |0 n-m ⟩), (20)where |ϕ d ⟩ is defined from x d as in Eq.",
    "Then, we jointly execute all the U d(CSP) circuits.w-1 d=0 U d(CSP) w-1 d=0 (|ϕ d ⟩ ⊗ |0 n-m ⟩) = w-1 d=0 |ψ d ⟩ (21)We do not have sufficient ancillae to perform these circuits in parallel, so we perform them with some \"indentation\" k between each other.",
    "That is, we begin the d = 0 protocol at layer 0, the d = 1 protocol at layer k, the d = 2 protocol at layer 2k, etc."
